Part 364



Proposed part 364 contains general provisions that would be applicable to the SILS and CIL programs, authorized by
parts B and C, respectively, of chapter 1 of title VII of the Act. In addition, some provisions in proposed part 364 also
are made specifically applicable to the OIB program authorized by chapter 2 of title VII of the Act.

