Proposed  366.44(h) would stay a Director's decision to terminate funds as of the date that the center files
a formal written appeal with the Secretary. 
Proposed  366.45 describes the procedures that a Director would have to follow upon receipt of a copy of the formal
written appeal that the center files with the Secretary. 
